OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight rain
OL,6,Fclears most areas except the far south
OL,7,Fbefore returning north later.
OL,8,FElsewhere clear spells with northern
OL,9,Fshowers, wintry on hills. Patchy frost
OL,10,Fin Scotland, Northern Ireland and
OL,11,FEngland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FStorm Dave moves northwards
OL,14,Facross Northern Ireland and western
OL,15,FScotland, bring cloud, rain and strong
OL,16,Fwinds. Coastal gales likely here, but
OL,17,Fdrier further south. Stay windy but
OL,18,Fmild.
